{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"nonorganic-functional-leopard","description":"## Summary\n\n`tests/external/test_ref_lock_ac0_live.py` pushes a throwaway `refs/reconciler/spike-*`\nref to the `origin` remote to prove the ref-lock round-trip \"against the actual origin\".\nThat assumes a **writable** `origin`. In this repo code lands via Gerrit and GitHub\n`origin` is a **read-only mirror** — the external-integration Actions token is\n`contents: read` and `github-actions[bot]` gets 403 on push. The test was added\n2026-07-04 (after the last green run 2026-06-16) and has therefore **never passed** in\nthis workflow; it was masked by the ALLOW_MODEL_REQUESTS guard until that was fixed.\n\nIts assumption (a writable non-ticket-branch remote) is invalid for this repo, so the\ntest should be removed. The hermetic counterpart\n`tests/unit/rebar_reconciler/state/test_ref_lock.py::test_ac0_blob_ref_roundtrips_through_remote`\nalready proves the acquire/release/read CAS mechanics against a local bare remote, so\nremoving the live variant loses no real coverage.\n\n## Reproduction Steps\n\n1. Trigger the external-integration workflow (external job) on main.\n2. Observe test_ref_lock_ac0_live fail: `git push ... origin refs/reconciler/spike-* -> exit 128`,\n   `remote: Permission to navapbc/rebar.git denied to github-actions[bot]` / 403.\n\nExpected: the external job is green.\nActual: the test fails because origin is not writable in this CI.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Delete tests/external/test_ref_lock_ac0_live.py.\n- [ ] The hermetic unit test (test_ref_lock.py) remains and still covers the CAS mechanics.\n- [ ] Verified end-to-end: the external-integration GitHub Action's external job runs green.","id":"0de0-4d1e-22b5-455a","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"remove stale test_ref_lock_ac0_live: assumes a writable origin remote (invalid in a Gerrit/read-only-mirror repo)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783658179884806001,"uuid":"2199902b-8bdd-4280-9cbd-db3d652bbf35"}